null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1000559, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O God, bless Muhammad and his Household, make us go to the repentance that Thou lovest and make us leave the persistence that Thou hatest! O God, when we halt before two decreases, in religion or in this world, let the decrease fall upon that which passes quickly and relent in that which lasts the longer!", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Ay Allah! Rehmat naazil farma Hazrat Muhammad (s.a.w.a) aur unki Aal (a.s) par aur hamari tawajjoh us tauba ki taraf kar de jo Tujhe pasand hai aur gunah par gunah karne se hamein dur rakh jo Tujhe na-pasand hai. Baare Ilaaha! Jab hamara iraada kuchh aisa ho keh (hamari kisi kotaahi ke sabab) deen ka nuqsaan hota ho ya duniya ka, to nuqsaan (duniya mein) qaraar de keh jo jald fana hone waala hai, aur afwa o maafi ko (deen ke maamle mein) qaraar de jo baaqi o bar-qaraar rehne waala hai.", "Urdu": "اے اللہ! رحمت نازل فرما محمد اوران کی آل پر اور ہماری توجہ اس کی توبہ کی طرف مبذول کر دے جو تجھے پسند ہے اورگناہ کے اصرار سے ہمیں دور رکھ جو تجھے ناپسند ہے بارالہا!جب ہمارا موقف کچھ ایسا ہو کہ (ہماری کسی کوتاہی کے باعث) دین کا زیاں ہوتا ہو یا دنیا کا تو نقصان (دنیا میں ) قرار دے کہ جو جلد فنا پذیر ہے اورعفو ودرگذر کو(دین کے معاملہ میں ) قرار دے جو باقی و برقرار رہنے والا ہے۔", "RArabic": "INSHA-ALLAH COMING SOON", "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰهُمَّ صَلِّ عَلٰى مُحَمَّدٍ وَّاٰلِهٖ وَصَيِّرْنَا اِلٰى مَحْبُوْبِكَ مِنَ التَّوْبَةِ وَاَزِلْنَا عَنْ مَكْرُوْهِكَ مِنَ الْاِصْرَارِ۔ اَللّٰهُمَّ وَمَتٰى وَقَفْنَا بَيْنَ نَقْصَيْنِ فِيْ دِيْنٍ اَوْ دُنْيَا فَاَوْقِعِ النَّقْصَ بِاَسْرَعِهِمَا فَنَاۗءً وَاجْعَلِ التَّوْبَةَ فِيْ اَطْوَلِهِمَا بَقَاۗءً۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1001653, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "When we set out after two concerns, one of which makes Thee pleased with us and the other of which displeases Thee, incline us toward that which makes Thee pleased and weaken our strength in that which displeases Thee! Leave not our souls alone to choose in that, for they choose falsehood except inasmuch as Thou givest success, and they command to evil except inasmuch as Thou hast mercy!", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Aur jab ham aise do kaamo ka iraada kare keh un mein se ek Teri khushnoodi ka aur dusra Teri naraazgi ka sabab ho to hamein us kaam ki taraf maayel kar jo Tujhe khush karne waala ho, aur us kaam se hamein rok de jo Tujhe naraaz karne waala ho (yaani na kare) aur is mauqe par hamein ikhteyaar de kar azaad na chhod de, kyu’n ki nafs to baatil ko hi pasand karne waala hai magar jahan Teri taufiq shaamil-e-haal ho aur buraayi ka hukm dene waala hai magar jahan Tera rahem kaam kar raha ho.", "Urdu": " اورجب ہم ایسے دو کاموں کا ارادہ کریں کہ ان میں سے ایک تیری خوشنودی کا اور دوسرا تیری ناراضی کا باعث ہو تو ہمیں اس کام کی طرف مائل کرنا جو تجھے خوش کرنے والا ہو۔ اور اس کام سے ہمیں بے دست وپا کر دینا جو تجھے ناراض کرنے والا ہو اور اس مرحلہ پر ہمیں اختیار دے کر آزاد نہ چھوڑ دے، کیونکہ نفس تو باطل ہی کو اختیار کرنے والا ہے۔ مگرجہاں تیری توفیق شامل حال ہو اوربرائی کا حکم دینے والا ہے مگر جہاں تیرا رحم کار فرما ہو۔", "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": "وَاِذَا هَمَمْنَا بِهَمَّيْنِ يُرْضِيْكَ اَحَدُهُمَا عَنَّا وَيُسْخِطُكَ الْاٰخَرُ عَلَيْنَا فَمِلْ بِنَا اِلٰى مَا يُرْضِيْكَ عَنَّا وَاَوْهِنْ قُوَّتَنَا عَمَّا يُسْخِطُكَ عَلَيْنَا وَلَا تُخَلِّ فِيْ ذٰلِكَ بَيْنَ نُفُوْسِنَا وَاخْتِيَارِهَا فَاِنَّهَا مُخْتَارَةٌ لِلْبَاطِلِ اِلَّا مَا وَفَّقْتَ اَمَّارَةٌ بِالسُّوْۗءِ اِلَّا مَا رَحِمْتَ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1001654, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O God, thou created us from frailty, built us up from feebleness, and began us from a mean water; we have no force except through Thy strength and no strength except through Thy help. So, confirm us by giving us success, point us the right way by Thy pointing, blind the eyes of our hearts toward everything opposed to Thy love, and set not in any of our limbs passage to disobeying Thee!", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Baare Ilaaha! Tu ne hamein kamzor aur sust paiyda kiya hai aur paani ke ek haqeer katre (nutfe) se khalq farmaaya hai agar hamein kuchh quwwat o taaqat haasil hai to Teri quwwat ki ba-daulat aur ikhteyaar hai to Teri madad ke sahare se, lehaaza apni taufiq se hamein sambhaal le aur apni rehnumaayi se taaqat o quwwat ataa kar aur hamare dil ki aankho’n ko us baato’n se jo Teri mohabbat ke khilaaf hai andha kar de aur hamare jism ke kisi hisse mein maasiyyat ke asar karne ki gunjaaish paiyda na kar.", "Urdu": "بارالہا! تو نے ہمیں کمزور اور سست بنیاد پیدا کیا ہے اور پانی کے ایک حقیر قطرہ (نطفہ ) سے خلق فرمایا ہے اگر ہمیں کچھ قوت وتصرف حاصل ہے تو تیری قوت کی بدولت اوراختیار ہے تو تیری مدد کے سہارے سے۔ لہذا اپنی توفیق سے ہماری دستگیری فرما اوراپنی رہنمائی سے استحکام و قوت بخش اورہمارے دیدہ دل کو ان باتوں سے جو تیری محبت کے خلاف ہیں نابینا کردے اورہمارے اعضاء کے کسی حصہ میں معصیت کے سرایت کرنے کی گنجائش پیدا نہ کر۔", "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰهُمَّ وَاِنَّكَ مِنَ الضُّعْفِ خَلَقْتَنَا وَعَلَى الْوَهْنِ بَنَيْتَنَا وَمِنْ مَاۗءٍ مَهِيْنٍ ابْتَدَاتَنَا فَلَا حَوْلَ لَنَا اِلَّا بِقُوَّتِكَ وَلَا قُوَّةَ لَنَا اِلَّا بِعَوْنِكَ فَاَيِّدْنَا بِتَوْفِيْقِكَ وَسَدِّدْنَا بِتَسْدِيْدِكَ وَاَعْمِ اَبْصَارَ قُلُوْبِنَا عَمَّا خَالَفَ مَحَبَّتَكَ وَلَا تَجْعَلْ لِشَيْ‏ءٍ مِنْ جَوَارِحِنَا نُفُوْذًا فِيْ مَعْصِيَتِكَ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1001655, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O God, bless Muhammad and his Household and assign the whisperings of our hearts, the movements of our members, the glances of our eyes, and the idioms of our tongues, to that which makes incumbent Thy reward, lest a good deed slip by us, through which we might deserve Thy repayment, or an evil deed remain with us, by which we might merit Thy punishment!", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Baare Ilaaha! Rehmat naazil farma Hazrat Muhammad (s.a.w.a) aur unki Aal (a.s) par aur hamare dil ke khayaalo’n, jism ke hisso’n ki harkato’n, aankh ke ishaaro’n aur zabaan ke jumlo’n ko un cheezo’n mein istemaal karne ki taufiq de jo Tere sawaab ka sabab ho, yahan tak keh hamse koi aisi neki chutne na paaye jis mein ham Tere ajr o sawaab ke mustahaq qaraar na paaye, aur na ham mein koi buraayi rahe jaaye jiski wajah se Tere azaab ke mustahaq thaiyre.", "Urdu": "بارالہا! رحمت نازل فرما محمد اورانکی آل پر اورہمارے دل کے خیالوں، اعضاء کی جنبشوں،آنکھ کے اشاروں اورزبان کے کلموں کو ان چیزوں میں صرف کرنے کی توفیق دے جو تیرے ثواب کا باعث ہوں یہاں تک کہ ہم سے کوئی ایسی نیکی چھوٹنے نہ پائے جس سے ہم تیرے اجر وثواب کے مستحق قرار پائیں۔ اورنہ ہم میں کوئی برائی رہ جائے جس سے تیرے عذاب کے سزاوار ٹھہریں۔", "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰهُمَّ فَصَلِّ عَلٰى مُحَمَّدٍ وَّاٰلِهٖ وَاجْعَلْ هَمَسَاتِ قُلُوْبِنَا وَحَرَكَاتِ اَعْضَائِنَا وَلَمَحَاتِ اَعْيُنِنَا وَلَهَجَاتِ اَلْسِنَتِنَا فِيْ مُوْجِبَاتِ ثَوَابِكَ حَتّٰى لَا تَفُوْتَنَا حَسَنَةٌ نَسْتَحِقُّ بِهَا جَزَاۗءَكَ وَلَا تَبْقٰى لَنَا سَيِّئَةٌ نَسْتَوْجِبُ بِهَا عِقَابَكَ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": nul